import './NavBar.css'
import { AppBar, Box, Toolbar, Typography, IconButton, Badge } from '@mui/material'
import { Facebook, Instagram, X, WatchLater, Email } from '@mui/icons-material'


function SocialMediaIcons() {
  return (
    <>
      <IconButton size="large" color="success">
        <Badge>
          <Facebook />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
      <IconButton size="large" color="success">
        <Badge>
          <Instagram />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
      <IconButton size="large" color="success">
        <Badge>
          <X />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
    </>
  )
}

export default function NavBar() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }} >
      <AppBar sx={{ bgcolor: "#FFFFFF" }} className="AppBar">
        <Typography
          className="NavBar"
          variant="h6"
          noWrap
          component="div"
          sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', sm: 'block' } }}
        >
          <IconButton size="large" color="success">
            <Badge>
              <WatchLater />
            </Badge>
          </IconButton>
          Mon - Sat: 8am - 6pm
          <IconButton size="large" color="success">
            <Badge>
              <Email />
            </Badge>
          </IconButton>
          davidsgardeningservicesmedway@gmail.com
        </Typography>
        <SocialMediaIcons />
      </AppBar>
    </Box >
  )
}
